title: Start
body:
Mitchell: Good day.
Te Rangitukehu: Kia ora. Who are you?
Mitchell: My name is Henry Mitchell, and I am Land Purchase Officer for the Crown.
Te Rangitukehu: Oh yeah. And what do you want with us?

[[I would like to talk to you about purchasing your land.|Mitchell_AskToBuy]]

title: Mitchell_AskToBuy
body: I would like to talk to you about purchasing some of your land.
